==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: odorant
<hw>o"dor*ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An odorous
substance;</def> <specif>especially,</specif> <def>a substance with a
strong odor added to a dangerous substance, such as natural gas, to
provide an easy detection method and a warning; <as>as, ethyl mercaptan
is used as an <ex>odorant</ex> in natural gas and propane to facilitate
detection of leaks</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Odorate</ent>⟦br⟧
